%N A218657 Number of n X 2 binary arrays with every 0 a king-move neighbor to some 1.
%H A218657 R. H. Hardin, <a href="/A218657/b218657.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..210</a>
%H A218657 <a href="/index/Rec#order_03">Index entries for linear recurrences with constant coefficients</a>, signature (3,3,3).
%F A218657 Empirical: a(n) = 3*a(n-1) + 3*a(n-2) + 3*a(n-3).
%F A218657 Empirical g.f.: 3*x*(1 + x)^2 / (1 - 3*x - 3*x^2 - 3*x^3). - _Colin Barker_, Mar 10 2018
%F A218657 The above empirical formulas confirmed using the transfer matrix method. - _Andrew Howroyd_, Jul 18 2026
